lin

31 八月, 2020, 13:38

大綱

use ../transfer/work_new_v3,clear
forvalues idx=1/6 {
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_eqg_me") mean  eqg
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_g_me") mean  g  
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_eqg_md") p50  eqg
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_g_md") p50  g  
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_eqg_umd") up50  eqg  
  tobin y`idx',gen("y`idx'_g_umd") up50  g  
}

  gen y=y1+y2+y3+y4+y5+y6
  tobin y,gen("y_eqg_me") mean  eqg
  tobin y,gen("y_g_me") mean  g  
  tobin y,gen("y_eqg_md") p50  eqg
  tobin y,gen("y_g_md") p50  g  
  tobin y,gen("y_eqg_umd") up50  eqg  
  tobin y,gen("y_g_umd") up50  g

y1 - y6個別

看個數

  • 顏色
    • 平均:red
    • 中間值:green
    • 僅僅只有個別的中間值:black
    • 眾值: blue
forvalues idx=1/6 {
qui uniqMiddle y`idx'

local ylabel : variable label y`idx'
histogram y`idx', percent ///
              xline(`r(mean)', lcolor(red)) ///
              xline(`r(p50)', lcolor(green)) ///
              xline(`r(up50)', lcolor(black)) ///
              title("`ylabel'") ///
              xla(`r(mean)' "mn" `r(p50)' "md" `r(up50)' "umd" )  
              

genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/") autoinc  
graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace 

  barClass y`idx',over(y`idx'_*)
  genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/") autoinc  
    graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace       
}

    graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace

都是1





local idx 1
foreach sep in me md umd{
  foreach opr in eqg g{
    capture safedrop my`idx'
    local ylabel "`=cond("`opr'"=="eqg","大等","大於")'`=cond("`sep'"=="me","平均",cond("`sep'"=="md","中間","獨中間"))'"
    modelbin y1_`opr'_`sep' y2_`opr'_`sep' y3_`opr'_`sep' y4_`opr'_`sep' y5_`opr'_`sep' y6_`opr'_`sep',gen(my`idx') label("`ylabel'") 
   disp "`ylabel'"
    local ++idx
  }
}

  barClass y,over(my*)
  genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/") autoinc  
  graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace

圖

//改成號碼用,提醒用而已 local idx 1 foreach sep in me md umd{ foreach opr in eqg g{ capture safedrop my_idx'_opr’_`sep’

modelbin y1_opr'_sep’ y2_opr'_sep’ y3_opr'_sep’ y4_opr'_sep’ y5_opr'_sep’ y6_opr'_sep’,gen(my_opr'_sep’) label("allidx'_opr’_`sep’") local ++idx } }

barClass y,over(my_*) genfilename “$outposix”,post(.png) autoinc
graph export `r(fn)’, as(png) replace

解釋
my 代表logist 模型用的0和1
例如:
my_eqg_me: 六項都>=平均值
my_g_md: 六項都> 中間值

總和呢

把Y1到Y6的分數加總成為Y,然後根據不同的值分類。



qui uniqMiddle y
histogram y, percent ///
              xline(`r(mean)', lcolor(red)) ///
              xline(`r(p50)', lcolor(green)) ///
              xline(`r(up50)', lcolor(black)) ///
              xline(`r(mode)', lcolor(blue)) ///
              title("`ylabel'") ///
              xla(`r(mean)' "mn" `r(p50)' "md" `r(up50)' "umd" `r(mode)' "mode")  
              

genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/")  autoinc  
graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace 

  barClass y,over(y_*)
  genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/") autoinc  
    graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace       

  barClass y,over(y_*) on(mean)
  genfilename "$outposix",post(.png) pre("report/") autoinc  
    graph export `r(fn)', as(png) replace

global xcont child wesmed  incom age104

 forvalues idx=1/6{  
  local mtitle :variable label my`idx' 
  eststo `mtitle':estpost tabstat $xcont $xcat $xalt, by(my`idx') statistics(count mean)  columns(statistics) 
 }
